  "text": "Urease was exited almost bacteria, fungi and higher plant. It is one kind of amidase, which could catalyze the hydrolysis of urea into carbon dioxide and ammonia. The activity of soil urease was positively correlated to the amount of microorganisms, organic material content, total nitrogen and available phosphorus (Chacón et al., 2009; [CITATION_1] .",
